We didn't detect a valid phone number.
Please go back to the previous screen and enter your phone 
number in full international format:
		1.Choose your country from country list. This will
		automatically fill the country code.

		2.Enter your phone number. Omit any leading 0s before 
		 the phone number.
For example, a correct United States phone number will
appear as +1 (408) 555-1234 after being entered.
